chuckeles.sstasker.model

Class Spaceship

  • java.lang.Object
    • chuckeles.sstasker.model.Spaceship

  • public class Spaceship
extends java.lang.Object
    The main model of the spaceship. Singleton. Contains the list of spaceship parts, tasks, crew members and inventory items.
